is available up to   November 30:
http://www.springer.com/birkhauser/mathematics/journal/11787

Special issues of the journal expected on the
following topics:

- Logic diagrams
- Multimodal logics
>>>>> Categorical logics <<<<<
- Hexagon of opposition

Among the many interesting papers published since the start of the journal =
